# Bank API - FastAPI Project

REST API developed with FastAPI to simulate a simple banking system.

## Features

- Create users
- Create accounts
- List users and accounts
- Deposit money
- Transfer money between accounts
- Data persistence with SQLite
- API versioning (`/api/v1`)
- Automatic documentation with Swagger

## Technologies used

- Python
- FastAPI
- SQLAlchemy
- SQLite
- Uvicorn

